{"tid":1699701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港靠你班暴徒區區開花食撚得屎啦","createTime":"2019-11-08T06:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T00:51:29.000Z","uid":313635,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"296b3884e659fcf02bac461e708099971991d60d","tid":1699701,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:34:08.000Z","msg":"我屌哂你地老母呀，乜撚嘢搞區區開花<br />\n你老味我第二日唔洗返工呀，你班甲曱日撚日喺度搞事破壞法治 屌你老母臭西<br />\n我警告你地呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪撚<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搞地鐵下面d月台幕門呀，消防設備間房呀，d電鑬呀，信號燈，仲有路軌呀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地鐵日日成百萬人次，你班暴徒成日搞，即係迫我地香港人罷工罷課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痴撚線㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我星期一要返工架，你咁搞係咪要全香港人唔返工同你地班甲曱攬炒呀<br />\n<br />\n你班仆街咁搞，政府遲早搞個獨立調查委員會清算你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0655611aefdde59fe3e775dc9df278d15d36c21","tid":1699701,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712dac5bf452eeeac7f8570384c7473291f849dc","tid":1699701,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:35:27.000Z","msg":"推呀 屌你"},{"pid":"8ba7f8672ba40ccc04a391ed4589a4dc8afd3e3e","tid":1699701,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:35:42.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"afe21055053e1a193305ce75393f752d2c62baa4","tid":1699701,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/